Multiport interactive demo for ctx

The top-level folder does a build for the systme with pkg-config
provided packages, the projects in the subfolders expect a built
ctx containing a ctx.h to exist before their build-systems are
invoked.

Ports:
  wasm         runs as an applet in browser
  esp32c3      with gc9a01 display and csxxx touch
  esp32c3-ssh  same as above with ssh terminal 
  flow3r       cccamp 2023 badge

Features:
  high level immediate mode ui toolkit
     button
     text
     entry
     slider
     focus, interaction apart from text-entry usable with left,right,return,esc
  demos of drawing with ctx

  only for some ports:
    wifi connect
    ssh, terminal

